                <h3>What are Deerflies?</h3>
                <p>
                    Deer flies are a type of horse fly that target the head and neck of its victims, both animal and human,
                    leaving a painful bite to which many are allergic. They are active in the summer months in northern USA and Canada.
                </p>
                <img src="" />
                <img src="" />
            </div>
        </div>

