            <div class="content foreground-text centered">
                <h3>
                    Deer flies are also known as:
                </h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Marsh Flies</li>
                    <li>Sheep Flies</li>
                    <li>Yellow Flies</li>
                    <li>Pine Flies</li>
                    <li>Strawberry Flies</li>
                    <li>May Flies</li>
                    <li>Greenheads</li>
                </ul>
